T1  - Time series analysis of COVID-19 infection curve: A change-point perspective
AU  - Jiang, Feiyu
AU  - Zhao, Zifeng
AU  - Shao, Xiaofeng
JO  - Journal of Econometrics
VL  - 232
IS  - 1
SP  - 1
EP  - 17
